# Input

```scss
$map:(key:(value),other-key:(nested:value));

$map-with-list:(key:(value,),other-key:(nested:value));

$nested-map:(key:(nested:value),other-key:(value));

```


# Formatted

```scss
$map: (
	key: (
		value,
	),
	other-key: (
		nested: value,
	),
);

$map-with-list: (
	key: (
		value,
	),
	other-key: (
		nested: value,
	),
);

$nested-map: (
	key: (
		nested: value,
	),
	other-key: (
		value,
	),
);

```
